 there was a beautiful princess named Cinderella. She lived with her wicked stepmother and two stepsisters. They treated Cinderella very badly. One day, they were invited to a grand ball in the Palace of Prince Charming, but since Cinderella has nothing to wear, her stepmother made her go to the cellar to get a pumpkin, and when she did, her stepsisters ripped off her clothes and turned her into a servant at the ball.</p>
